@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_rovfsm(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = wp.exp(wp.sin((v0 + 0.76 * tmp + 0.15)))
    v1 = (v0 * ((v0 + 0.77 + v1 + 0.16) - wp.abs(v2 + 0.43)))
    v2 = 0.46
    v0 = 0.55
    tmp = wp.exp((wp.sin(v2 + 0.98) - (v0 + 0.64 / tmp + 0.57)))
    v0 = 0.52
    tmp = ((wp.cos(v0 + 0.91) * v0) / wp.sin((tmp + 0.02 * tmp + 0.66)))
    v1 = tmp
    data[tid] = v0
